OL,3,CPlans for brand new Cornish secondary
OL,4,Cschool scrapped by Government
OL,6,FPlans for a new secondary school in
OL,7,FCornwall have been cancelled by the
OL,8,Fgovernment.
OL,10,FA spokesperson for the Department for
OL,11,FEducation said there was "not
OL,12,Fsufficient need" for additional school
OL,13,Fplaces to justify building a whole new
OL,14,Fschool.
OL,16,FThey added that the Government is
OL,17,F"committed" to making sure there are
OL,18,Fenough school places in Perranporth.
