OL,3,CPlans for brand new Cornish secondary
OL,4,Cschool scrapped by Government
OL,6,FThe cancellation is part of a wider
OL,7,F#3billion investment in new special
OL,8,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,9,F(SEND) provision, moving funding away
OL,10,Ffrom some planned mainstream schools.
OL,12,FThe planning permission had already
OL,13,Fbeen granted at the Liskey Hill site
OL,14,Ffor Perranporth Academy.
OL,16,FThe school should have opened in 2026
OL,17,Fand would've catered for 1,050
OL,18,Fstudents aged between 11 and 16.
