OL,3,CPlans for brand new Cornish secondary
OL,4,Cschool scrapped by Government
OL,6,FPerranzabuloe Parish Councillor Ben
OL,7,FByfield says the decision is "hugely
OL,8,Fdisappointing" adding that "as a
OL,9,Fcommunity, Perranporth has been
OL,10,Fcampaigning for this school for so
OL,11,Flong and not just for Perranporth, but
OL,12,Ffor the other surrounding villages of
OL,13,FSt Agnes, Goonhavern and Cubert,
OL,14,Fthere's a big catchment area for this
OL,15,Fschool and we've worked so hard over
OL,16,Fthe last five, ten years to try and
OL,17,Fbring this project to fruition."
