OL,3,CPlans for brand new Cornish secondary
OL,4,Cschool scrapped by Government
OL,6,FCornwall Council will be challenging
OL,7,Fthis decision and providing the
OL,8,FDepartment for Education with more
OL,9,Finformation.
OL,11,FCllr Byfield says that with the
OL,12,Fsupport from parents and from the
OL,13,Flocal community they'll be "pushing
OL,14,Fback against this decision" too.
OL,16,FDr Jennifer Blunden who leads Truro
OL,17,Fand Penwith Academy Trust, who were
OL,18,Fset to run Perranporth Academy, called
OL,19,Fthe decision "short-sighted".
