OL,3,CPlans for brand new Cornish secondary
OL,4,Cschool scrapped by Government
OL,6,FDr Blunden said "children from
OL,7,FPerranporth Primary School currently
OL,8,Fgo in 3 or 4 different directions.
OL,9,FSome go to Newquay schools, some go to
OL,10,FTruro schools and with the massive
OL,11,Fdevelopments in housing around, on the
OL,12,Foutskirts of Truro and around Newquay,
OL,13,Fthe situation is only going to get
OL,14,Fworse over the next few years.
OL,16,F"So we know that, working with the
OL,17,FLocal Authority, the sufficiency of
OL,18,Fplaces for secondary age pupils by the
OL,19,Fearly 2030's is going to mean that we
OL,20,Fabsolutely are going to be needing a
OL,21,Fnew school."
